Daily Kos Elections Iowa caucus liveblog thread #12

Feb 01, 2016 9:37pm PST by David Nir The Iowa caucuses are finally here, and we're liveblogging the first results of the 2016 presidential nominating contests. The caucuses start at 8 PM Eastern sharp (latecomers are not permitted to participate). As results come in, you can consult our guides to how the caucuses work and what to expect.
